      <div class="rbp-apps-section-head">
        <p class="rbp-apps-section-label">Common questions</p>
        <h2 class="rbp-apps-section-title">Applications FAQ</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="rbp-apps-faq" role="list">
        <details class="rbp-apps-faq-item" role="listitem">
          <summary class="rbp-apps-faq-q">
            How long does an application take to be reviewed?
            <span class="rbp-apps-faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="rbp-apps-faq-a">Most on-demand service purchases are processed immediately. Core Service intake forms are reviewed within 1 business day. Marketplace listings and Custom Solutions requests involve a manual review that typically takes 2–3 business days.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="rbp-apps-faq-item" role="listitem">
          <summary class="rbp-apps-faq-q">
            Do I need to be a member to apply?
            <span class="rbp-apps-faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="rbp-apps-faq-a">Most services are available to all customers. Membership unlocks priority access, exclusive rates, partner offers, and accelerated review timelines. Marketplace listings have a member priority queue.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="rbp-apps-faq-item" role="listitem">
          <summary class="rbp-apps-faq-q">
            What happens after I submit a Core Service intake form?
            <span class="rbp-apps-faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="rbp-apps-faq-a">Our team will review your intake form and match you to the appropriate service and consultant. You'll receive a confirmation email and a follow-up within 1 business day to confirm your engagement details and next steps.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="rbp-apps-faq-item" role="listitem">
          <summary class="rbp-apps-faq-q">
            Can I apply for multiple services at once?
            <span class="rbp-apps-faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="rbp-apps-faq-a">Yes. You can purchase multiple on-demand services or submit applications for different pathways simultaneously. Our team coordinates delivery across engagements where needed.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="rbp-apps-faq-item" role="listitem">
          <summary class="rbp-apps-faq-q">
            How does Business NBN availability work?
            <span class="rbp-apps-faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="rbp-apps-faq-a">Business NBN availability depends on your address and the infrastructure available in your area. Use the address checker on the Business NBN page to confirm availability. Some locations require a manual serviceability check by our team.</p>
        </details>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
